7. How NFTs and Tokens Change Ownership

NFTs and tokens have created a new form of ownership. Digital assets can now be owned, traded, and verified directly on the blockchain without intermediaries like banks or companies. Creators can receive royalties automatically whenever their NFTs are resold. Fungible tokens enable decentralized finance, making global transactions faster and more open.
